videos.description: Dom Maggio has his punt blocked by Deshawn Capers-Smith and Charles Oliver scoops it up for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Texas A&M scores first on blocked punt

videos.description: Dom Maggio has his punt blocked for the second time on two straight attempts.
videos.headline: Wake Forest gets 2nd consecutive punt blocked

videos.description: Nick Starkey runs a play-action fake and then finds Christian Kirk down field for a 42-yard completion. Trayveon Williams scores a 2-yard touchdown on the next play.
videos.headline: Texas A&M rolling early with 2nd TD

videos.description: Demon Deacons' QB Jonh Wolford fires a quick pass to Scotty Washington who beats his defender for a 50-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wake Forest answers back with big TD

videos.description: Wake Forest's QB John Wolford fires the pass to Tabari Hines on the quick slant for a 7-yard touchdown and ties the game 14-14 against the Aggies.
videos.headline: Wolford throws 2nd TD to tie Aggies

videos.description: RB Matt Colburn takes the handoff and turns up the speed going 66-yards into the redzone.
videos.headline: Demon Deacons' Colburn shows sweet feet on big run

videos.description: QB John Wolford launches a pass downfield and Scotty Washington makes the leaping grab between two defenders for a 37-yard gain.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Washington makes incredible catch

videos.description: John Wolford throws a fade route to Tabari Hines and Hines makes the diving grab for a 7-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wolford-Hines connection leads to Wake Forest TD

videos.description: Jessie Bates sees a gap and races up the field untouched for a 59-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wake executes punt return perfectly for TD

videos.description: QB Nick Starkel finds WR Christian Kirk streaking down the middle of the field and he scampers in for a 52-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Aggies not done yet after Kirk TD catch

videos.description: John Wolford finds TE Cam Serigne who beats his defender and takes it in for a 37-yard touchdown to go up 38-21 against the Aggies.
videos.headline: Wolford's 4th TD extends Wake Forest lead

videos.description: QB Nick Starkel throws the pass to Christian Kirk and Kirk shows good reflexes by catching the ball off of his facemask.
videos.headline: Aggies' Kirk makes odd TD  catch off helmet

videos.description: QB Nick Starkel throws a short pass to Christian Kirk who breaks a tackle for a 9-yard touchdown
videos.headline: Kirk scores 3rd TD with vicious stiff-arm for Aggies

videos.description: RB Trayveon Williams shows his speed bursting up the field for a 43-yard gain.
videos.headline: Aggies' RB Williams rips off nice run

videos.description: John Wolford tries to escape pressure but is sacked by Deshawn Capers-Smith and Anthony Hines lll recovers it for the Aggies.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's offense commits costly turnover

videos.description: On 4th down, John Wolford takes the read option and pitches it to RB Cade Carney for a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wake Forest gambles and it pays off with TD

videos.description: Nick Starkel throws it into tight coverage but WR Jhamon Ausbon is able to make the catch for the 13-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Aggies take late lead on Starkel-to-Ausbon TD

videos.description: Demon Deacons' RB Matt Colburn runs up the right side and scores a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wake Forest strikes back with rush TD

videos.description: The Demon Deacons outlasted Texas A&M in a shootout to win the Belk Bowl 55-52 against the Aggies.
videos.headline: Wake Forest beats Texas A&M in a thriller
